{
  "texts": [
    " The Role of Artificial Intelligence: Like the mentioned uses in the pre-design stage, textbased artificial intelligence can assist in tasks such as scheduling, document management, and project progress tracking (Chaillou, 2019), This is achieved by leveraging a variety of its patterns.",
    " Goal-Driven Systems: This pattern aids in analyzing data from previous projects to determine cost, timelines, and predict the requirements of future projects.",
    "This helps ensure the accuracy and completeness of specifications, saving a significant amount of time.",
    " Recognition Pattern: This pattern assists in completing design documents by recognizing similar details in the database and utilizing them.",
    " Autonomous Systems Pattern: Self-operating systems help in finalizing design documents, starting from hand-drawn sketches and data, transforming them into detailed execution drawings and comprehensive design documents."
  ]
}